msgid "Erinnerungsintervall (Tage)"
msgstr "Reminder interval (days)"

#: Collection_Management_System/runtime_settings.py:120
msgid ""
"Frühestens nach so vielen Tagen wird für dieselbe Ausleihe erneut erinnert."
msgstr "The same loan is reminded again after this many days at the earliest."

